Basic Installation
==================

	To compile this, you need the development packages (files) of 
xfce4-panel, if xfce4 has been installed from source yo probably need
anything. A C compiler (gcc, for example), gmake (gnu-make), and the 
gnu-toolchain (autoconf, automake,etc..) to build screenshooter from 
svn or cvs imports.

From CVS o SVN
==========================

You need run in the xfce4-screenshooter-plugin directory.

$ sh autogen.sh

The following instructions must be applied to sources from cvs origin or tarball origin.

$./configure

$gmake or (make)

$make install

For Debian and FreeBSD users there are a debian and FreeBSD directory to make a package, 
from sources.

